# user pov
- create a book
  - title
  - list chapters

- delete a book

- mark a chapter done

- unmark a chapter done

# tables
book
- id
- title

chapter (ordering is defined by id)
- id
- book_id
- title
- read_at

# api

get all books (just titles)
get book (and chapters)
create book (and chapters)
delete book
mark chapter done
unmark chapter done


# v2+
- edit book titles, chapter titles, chapter order, add/remove chapters
- chapter length
- chapter hierarchy
